There are multiple Labs working on Robotic Related Problems and offering Robotics Teaching.
This Site is a short overwiev of available lectures and practicals and how the TriPed is involved with them.
All of these Institutions are part of the <a href="https://www.ziti.uni-heidelberg.de/ziti/en/institute/research"> Ziti</a>, which offers the nonconsecutive Master  <a href="https://www.ziti.uni-heidelberg.de/ziti/de/studium/msc-ti/502-profil-des-studiengangs"> computer engineering </a>.
The Master offeres a specialisation in Robotics with which multiple of these courses are acosiated with.
It should be noted however that most of these courses are also applicable to physics, maths and computer science students, please check your "modulhandbuch" for more information.



# ARIES Lab
Professor Masias <a href="https://www.lorenzomasia.com/lab-and-people">Aries Lab</a> is the home of the TriPed Robot.
